body_html:
@asimshankar, I got this when run the speech demo in Android Studio3:
Caused by: java.io.IOException: Not a valid TensorFlow Graph serialization: Shape must be rank 1 but is rank 0 for 'Mfcc' (op: 'Mfcc') with input shapes: [16000,0,257], [].

and I unzip the apk file I generated in Android Studio found that there's no libtensorflow_demo.so in libs directory.

How ever the "tensorflow_demo.apk" (which is the prebuilt Android demo applications) I download from "https://ci.tensorflow.org/view/Nightly/job/nightly-android/" runs ok.

confuse a lot about that
